title: Guardians of the Galaxy (001 - 020 + TPBs & Extras) ( 2013 -
description:
Guardians of the Galaxy (001 - 020 + TPBs & Extras) ( 2013 - Ongoing)(Zone-Empire)



A Marvel NOW! title featuring Star-Lord, Gamora, Drax the Destroyer, Rocket Raccoon, Groot and Iron Man as The Guardians of the Galaxy. After Age of Ultron it also introduced Angela to the Marvel Universe.

During the All-New Marvel NOW! relaunches, Iron Man was replaced with Captain Marvel and Venom (Flash Thompson).

The original creative team consisted of writer Brian Michael Bendis and artist Steve McNiven
